  $}

  ${
    bitr3.1 $e |- ( ps <-> ph ) $.
    bitr3.2 $e |- ( ps <-> ch ) $.
    $( An inference from transitive law for logical equivalence. $)
    bitr3   $p |- ( ph <-> ch ) $=
